<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Weinheim, uns
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnd <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> rate die
                        nehst bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedigen
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem
                            <expan>pfallnczgrafe<ex>n</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Stepf<ex>an</ex></expan>, seins <expan>brud<ex>er</ex>s</expan>,
                                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sein, wol gesagt, wie ir ewch in
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> gar frewntlich und willig beweiset habt, des
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> danken und umb ewch
                                <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>schulden</expan>. Also <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir zu ewch <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>
                        credencie <expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dis</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
